-- ECB's Tumpel-Gugerell Says That Improvement in Loan Demand Is `Good News'
-- B y   C a r o l i n e   C o n n a n
-- 2010-09-27T18:00:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-27/ecb-s-tumpel-gugerell-says-that-improvement-in-loan-demand-is-good-news-.html
European Central Bank Executive
Board member Gertrude Tumpel-Gugerell said improving demand for
loans within the euro-region economy is “good news.” She spoke
to Bloomberg Television at a conference in Brussels today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Caroline Connan in London at 
